sources.description:
Sherlock Holmes sets out to discover why a trio of murderous villains, including a dangerously attractive female, are desperate to obtain three unassuming and inexpensive little music boxes.

Original title: Dressed to Kill (1946)
AKA: Prelude to Murder/Sherlock Holmes and the Secret Code
Colorized version: https://youtu.be/Z06G2jmMn0I

Director: Roy William Neill
Writers: Arthur Conan Doyle, Leonard Lee, Frank Gruber
Cast: Basil Rathbone, Nigel Bruce, Patricia Morison 
Genre:  Colorized classics, Crime, Mystery 

This video is available with audio in English, German, Italian & Spanish. And also subtitled in more than 30 languages. Click on ⚙️ and choose subtitles and/or audio tracks.
